high_descs: Turn left and walk to the counter in between the two sinks.
Pick up the dirty green washcloth that's in front of you between the sinks.
Take a step to your right then a small step backwards.
Wash the wash cloth in the sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Move back to where you got the wash cloth from.
Put the wash cloth back where you got it from.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean wash cloth on the counter.

high_descs: Turn to the left and face the counter between the counter between the two sinks.
Pick the cloth up from the counter.
Go right and turn to face the sink on the right side of the counter.
Put the cloth in the sink and turn the water on and then off and take the cloth out of the sink.
Put the cloth down on the counter between the two sinks.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean cloth on the counter.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the sinks.
Pick up the dirty blue rag.
Wash the rag in the right sink.
Place the rag on the counter between the sinks.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean rag on a counter.
